name huffman
category Package
revision 67071
shortdesc Drawing binary Huffman trees with MetaPost and METAOBJ
longdesc This MetaPost package allows to draw binary Huffman trees from
longdesc two arrays : an array of strings, and an array of weights
longdesc (numeric). It is based on the METAOBJ package which provides
longdesc many tools for building trees in general.
